-Title- 
Solange Shades ES Magazine For Touching Her Hair
-Keywords-
['body', 'solange', 'es', 'magazine', 'pdtthe', 'shades', 'hair', 'shared', 'touching', 'post', 'cover', 'act', 'oct']
-SUMMARY ARTICLE-
Solange Knowles has given the side eye to ES Magazine for touching her hair - or should we say removing?
A post shared by Evening Standard Magazine (@eveningstandardmagazine) on Oct 19, 2017 at 12:01am PDTThe photo editing is all the more surprising as in the interview that accompanies the shoot Solange spoke about how important her hair is to her as a means of expression.
