Man Arrested After Stealing Truckload Of Baby Formula
-Keywords-
['park', 'stolen', 'arrested', 'formula', 'truck', 'baby', 'truckload', 'warrants', 'westnsw', 'driving', 'stealing', 'pursuit', 'man']
