-Title- 
The Morning Wrap: Akhilesh Yadav's New Avatar; Yogi Adityanath Defines 'Ram Rajya'
-Keywords-
['yogi', 'yadavs', 'minister', 'adityanath', 'states', 'avatar', 'morning', 'akhilesh', 'wrap', 'defines', 'round', 'media', 'public', 'marriage', 'rajya', 'uttar', 'interesting', 'nominations', 'pradesh', 'ram']
