When the bride's father walked in the room and saw his daughter in her wedding dress, he was immediately overcome with emotions.
The bride thanked her father for the dress and for giving her the dream wedding.
In return, he simply said thank you for being such a wonderful daughter.
When her father heard of this, he took her there and bought both his daughters and his wife outfits from their favorite designer.
-TEXT INSIDE ARTICLE-
