-Title- 
This Woman Got A Wonder Woman Tattoo Over Her Double Mastectomy Scars
-Keywords-
['scars', 'mastectomy', 'told', 'double', 'stephanie_jane_kelly', 'stephanie', 'surgery', 'wonder', 'woman', 'kelly', 'shared', 'post', 'tattoo', 'breast']
