Recognising Self Worth After Cancer We know that cancer affects body image and a sense of self through physical symptoms like hair loss, skin damage and gaining or losing weight, which can change how you look and feel. But you can also lose your sense of self psychologically, as cancer can take complete control of your life and many people feel that suddenly they are defined by their cancer diagnosis. Chief Executive of cancer charity, Maggie's

