-Title- 
Woman Tracks Down Missing Cat After Uploading Its Photo To Tinder
-Keywords-
['reward', 'peanut', 'uploading', 'missing', 'killer', 'woman', 'search', 'katie', 'track', 'tracks', 'cat', 'tinder', 'went']
-SUMMARY ARTICLE-
A woman has been reunited with her missing moggy thanks to the power of Tinder.
Supplied Katie Alsop and her cat PeanutThe genius idea came about after Katie’s ginger and white puss, called Peanut, went missing overnight on 11 October.
