-Title- 
연설에서 기후변화를 언급한 시진핑의 이 말은 트럼프를 겨냥한 게 거의 확실하다
-Keywords-
['china', '트럼프를', 'beijing', 'great', '시진핑의', 'party', 'congress', '말은', '19th', '게', '이', '확실하다', '겨냥한', 'communist', 'hall', '기후변화를', '18', '언급한', '연설에서', '2017']
-SUMMARY ARTICLE-
The CPC opened the 19th National Congress at the Great Hall of the People Wednesday morning.
The Communist Party Congress happens only twice in a decade, and provides a glimpse into the world of Chinese politics.
The Chinese Communist Party opens its week-long, twice-a-decade congress in the Great Hall of the People.
The Chinese Communist Party opens its week-long, twice-a-decade congress in the Great Hall of the People.
China's Communist Party opened its 19th National Congress on October 18, a week-long, twice-a-decade political meeting to reshuffle leadership positions.
